br />\n重捨命要錫住所謂強國個心仔?<br />\n<br />\n出大事 無d低等人口幫佢打飛機<br />\n<br />\n就迫鳩我地安慰<br />\n<br />\non99</span></span>"},{"pid":"28486488a99aab49f6a4f8e6d9d11a2fe79150a9","tid":1854540,"uid":107577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T14:44:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n借位<br />\n[行動post] 武漢肺炎係上天賜比香港人打爆港共嘅機會，做嘢啦！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1838198\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1838198</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我要真雙普選<br />\n立刻去聯署！！</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hong-kong-universal-suffrage-plan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fhong-kong-universal-suffrage-plan&d=6xH2G4nGFyEJ53rX7DpuMZmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=d90db021\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hong-kong-universal-suffrage-plan</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Hong Kong Universal Suffrage Plan<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/56Kq4TS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F56Kq4TS.jpg&h=3605f423&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4c7972c131a6f81ce4f60369a4c73b7f8065dce1","tid":1854540,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T14:45:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nusoOoa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnusoOoa.jpg&h=d5f12261&s={SIZE}\" />： 不要罷工綁架民眾 <br />\n事件平息後慢慢坐低傾啦"},{"pid":"f97cd371541aeebfb651f7c43e966b12a3b71d20","tid":1854540,"uid":33498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T14:46:29.000Z","msg":"解散政府"},{"pid":"b33fa37bfa6ca33a80